<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Tom_Bearden" title="Tom Bearden" class="mw-redirect">Tom Bearden</a> announced the arrival of the MEG technology on March 26, 2002. This device was supposed to be in mass production by 2003, and claimed to produce unlimited energy from the vacuum, to answer mankind's power needs.</td>
